As Albino progressed deeper into the facility, the encounters with the soldiers became increasingly predictable. They appeared like clockwork, their movements rigid and mechanical as they sought to thwart his advance. But Albino was a force to be reckoned with, his formidable abilities rendering their efforts futile.

Bullets ricocheted off his skull with a metallic clang, their impact doing little more than momentarily halt his relentless stride or graze his forehead. Any wounds inflicted by stray shots on less durable Ã¡reas were quickly shrugged off, his powerful healing factor sealing the injuries shut with unnatural speed. As the soldiers opened fire, Albino moved with preternatural grace, weaving effortlessly between the hail of bullets as if they were nothing more than raindrops.
